<font face="Comic Sans MS, Lucida Sans, Helvetica">
<table bgcolor="white" align="right"> <tr><td bgcolor="white"><table>
<caption><font face="Comic Sans MS, Lucida Sans, Helvetica">Practising Before the Trip</font> <img src="../../gifs/smile.gif"></caption>
<tr><td>
